{"tid":1667256,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"林志偉指網上流傳指他不滿特首就警隊發表的言論是捏造","createTime":"2019-10-21T10:58:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T18:47:51.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"f450e192dd127b728f00872177453c22ba6fa072","tid":1667256,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T10:58:09.000Z","msg":"網上近日流傳一些圖片，指香港警察隊員佐級協會主席林志偉，不滿特首林鄭月娥就警隊行動發表的言論。<br />\n<br />\n林志偉今日發表聲明表示，有關圖片為虛假捏造，強烈譴責偽冒他發表意見和意圖誤導公眾的行為，表示會保留追究權利。<br />\n<br />\n聲明強調員佐級協會只會以具名的信函與其他個人或組織溝通，其他在網上匿名發放的資訊和圖片，都不代表協會立場。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1487481-20191021.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1487481-20191021.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=bp2T%2F%2B5c5q8hcpZmRI3qNhkIbV9%2FoY%2BmeTBoP0X2IjM%3D&h=ddf6a64c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1487481-20191021.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=06f94740\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1487481-20191021.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"3ec604513aaeea8e21c551676c57e3dafccd9415","tid":1667256,"uid":256019,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T10:59:56.000Z","msg":"國家主席林志偉，你今時今日仲有邊個使驚？話屌就屌啦！"},{"pid":"09d4db4178f11799c6dc779f14297395e8739eb4","tid":1667256,"uid":78039,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T11:01:46.000Z","msg":"總統政治意識叻過光頭佬咁多既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d5b30f0b6e250af6726df851e3a00ab3b74f465","tid":1667256,"uid":37869,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T11:02:52.000Z","msg":"咁即係滿唔滿意林鄭的言論？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ad86315cd1fe95bc7477b26ad237eca4f04d89f","tid":1667256,"uid":91259,"like":0,"disli